{"tid":26060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣食魚蛋燒賣","createTime":"2016-12-06T13:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-07T12:57:58.000Z","uid":57133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e809dc1e106e0fb6687e5203c606e1cc8627fec","tid":26060,"uid":57133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人去過世貿嗰邊嗰幾間街頭小食店食野，有嘅話一定會記得個呀姐<br />\n買一串送一串 煎釀三寶十蚊六件 行埋黎<br />\n呢排側邊嗰間都開始反擊<br />\n行過路過唔好錯過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68f68d4063011c6fb675f89e2df4be04c806ab6","tid":26060,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196adf3152d6ba08f00dffae034bf93c5187c108","tid":26060,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0314fec85673ce4057584858dd4183051ff8edbf","tid":26060,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"好似係move過去 但仲好生意過隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d92d511ab968578a5e0647e24bf9cac54eccf7","tid":26060,"uid":57133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街口個間有個黑口黑面 ，串過馬撚態度又差</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前做岩岩開嗰陣，佢做兩蚊一串魚蛋，都唔知放左咩入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cb64c4e22a68e39f9872f32b1baf4a8c3642db","tid":26060,"uid":57133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉角嗰間好食啲"},{"pid":"dccd88c0c943e5e8df2dd8a